{"tid":1830809,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【十大中文金曲】謝安琪冧莊最優秀流行女歌手：邊個時期嘅我都好真實","createTime":"2020-01-20T02:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T03:03:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b725254a78a8a8e9c518a27eac29f66f8262363","tid":1830809,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:04:13.000Z","msg":"本年最後一張樂壇成績表由港台頒發，今年港台取消了實體頒獎禮，改以錄製節目方式宣佈得獎者。<br />\n<br />\n最優秀流行男／女歌手由張敬軒和謝安琪冧莊，第二度獲此獎的謝安琪說：「邊個時期嘅我都好真實，呢個係累積返嚟嘅我，包括期許嘅我，想你哋認識嘅我，今年自己做咗好多新嘗試，自己係好正能量嘅人，演唱會以誤解為題材，自己係一個歌手，喺歌曲裏面哽咽會照唱，發脾氣就發脾氣，得到回應好多樣化，成日覺得創作如果牽動到大家情緒係好好，我覺得共鳴唔一定要經歷同一件事，做創作要真心，自己都要心跳冒汗，先有機會觸碰其他嘅心。」<br />\n<br />\n而「最佳樂隊／組合」的三甲分別是，銅獎：小塵埃；銀獎：Dear Jane；金獎：RubberBand，RB說：「今年出道十一年，隨時間我哋喺呢個城市做音樂，好多靈感係呢個城市畀我哋，變咗我哋嘅精神，首先要做嘢感動自己，再同聽眾講，呢個係我哋方向，樂迷多謝我哋，唔會覺得自己偉大，佢哋話覺得感動，令我哋好開心，最難得係我哋可以用廣東話分享諗法。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579443184_e1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579443184_e1c0.jpg&h=6229d3e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200119/large/1579443184_e57b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200119%2Flarge%2F1579443184_e57b.png&h=2ee29f4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200119/EYC7EG2OC7H7B6RK5IEEVT6CTM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200119%2FEYC7EG2OC7H7B6RK5IEEVT6CTM%2F&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BPyvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=d68debce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200119%2FEYC7EG2OC7H7B6RK5IEEVT6CTM%2F&h=a596ef87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200119/EYC7EG2OC7H7B6RK5IEEVT6CTM/</a>"},{"pid":"387